Package: CONSURE
Title: Estimating spatially continuous survival, migratory connectivity and recovery probability.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Saskia",
           family = "Schirmer",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "saskia.schirmer@uni-greifswald.de")
Description: This package estimates survival, migratory connectivity and recovery probability in continuous space from dead recovery data. The data can be simulated by the package or committed as a dataset. The package implements the continuous and combined approach described in detail in the dissertation of Saskia Schirmer.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/SaskiaSchirmer/CONSURE
